Mavic Pro or phantom 4?  Both are 4K drones so what's the difference well Phantom 4 has wider filming angle to capture more in a shot than the Mavic pro. Mavic Pro has the portability of a small purse and Phantom 4 is a carry on suit case. Phantom 4 has more durable structured design compared to the Mavic Pro folding portable design. Both have their advantage and disadvantages so the question is what are you using it for. What design best fits your needs. Do you need ultra portability with a great shot or do you need the best possible shot and portability is not a issue. The best device is the device that meets your needs The one you can have on you when you need it! So base your decision on what your needs are! #phantom4vsmavicpro #phantom4vsmavic
